                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Cumberland</placeName>\n                <date>June 19<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1854</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser Esq</addressee>:</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear sir: We <sic>belief</sic><lb/> it is interesting to you to hear\n                some times some<lb/> thing about the <sic>wellfare</sic> &amp; improving\n                con<lb/>dition of small congregations such as ours:<lb/> it gives me pleasure to\n                assure you that we<lb/> are spiritually &amp; <sic>finanzicaly</sic> prospering<lb/>\n                <sic>thoug</sic> there may be some indifferent ones,<lb/> the majority of our\n                    Cahl<add>?</add> are good determined<lb/> Jews whom nought could induce to\n                fall<lb/> back to the death like sleep of indifference.<lb/> By Order of our\n                President <persName>Mr S. Herdellerger</persName><lb/>, elected may last., I am to\n                inform you that our<lb/> Congregation is compelled to engage another<lb/> gentleman\n                to fill the vacancy of Chasan Shochet<lb/> &amp; Teacher occasioned by the timely\n                resignation of<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Wechsler</persName> our present functionary, as also<lb/> to advertise\n                in differen'd papers we have<lb/> agreed with <persName>Mr W.</persName> that he\n                will give up<lb/> the place at any time from the <date>first of August</date><lb/>\n                or earlier otherwise continue his functions a<lb/> month after expiration of the\n                Quarter being<lb/> to the <date>first of October</date> in case we are not able<lb/>\n                to fill the vacancy sooner. A single<lb/> man</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jh3dn8m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
