                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>man one of those generally emigrating from\n                <placeName><sic>germany</sic></placeName><lb/> to this <sic>contry</sic> we prefer\n                as expectation of such don't<lb/> overreact our ability, we pay 250.00 doll. you\n                will<lb/> please to insert in the Occident a Notice in general<lb/> that on\n                application to <persName>Frank</persName> &amp; <persName role=\"author\"\n                    >Adler</persName> further<lb/> particulars will be given, and charge to the\n                congregation<lb/> The accounts of the <sic>suffrings</sic> of our Brethren in<lb/>\n                <placeName>Erez Israel</placeName> have reached us, and <sic>dreadfull</sic><lb/>\n                &amp; <sic>heartsickning</sic>\n                <sic>the</sic> are indeed. An Appeal made<lb/> to our brethren <sic>hier</sic> was\n                heartily <sic>respondet</sic><lb/> to and from the result we are glad to send<lb/>\n                to you, the agent, the enclosed Draft for 50 dol<lb/> on the western Bank of Balto.\n                may this, little as it<lb/> is, contribute to alleviate such distress.</p>\n            <p>we fail the monthly appearance of your Occident<lb/> and swarming as this\n                    <sic>country</sic> is with proselyte<lb/> scrip, it cannot fail to refresh &amp;\n                strengthen<lb/> the mind of every israelitish reader, hoping<lb/> that you enjoy\n                good health, we take the<lb/> liberty to sign <sic>ourselfs</sic> your sincere\n                friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Henry Adler</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Secty of the <add>?</add> B. L Congregation</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
